\newlabel{tab:resolution}{{3.10}{56}{Svanstr\"om drone recall by RGB variant and inference size (one harness: stride-7 sample, $n=4{,}102$, IoP@0.5, conf $0.25$). Doubling \texttt {imgsz} lifts both variants by a similar increment ($+28$/$+25$~pp); the absolute level is set by the training stance, and the confuser-suppressing \texttt {retrained\_v2} is unusable on Svanstr\"om at either size}{table.caption.32}{}}
